<@U1W3MUNDB|amybriggs> uploaded a file: <https://gstudents.slack.com/files/amybriggs/F239PPGKY/img_2738.jpg|IMG_2738.JPG> and commented: Good morning outsiders, a shout-out to any runners in our group.  I run the Mesa Trail pretty much every Saturday, and would love company, if anyone's game.  I won't post it every week, so this is an open invite, hit me up if you want more info.  It's about 13.5 miles, with some good ups and downs, and I have to hike some of the hills and gnarlier technical bits - if you're used to running trails here, my pace is probably easy for you.  And yes, these pictures are to entice you join me.  It's good to get out and clear the jQuery cobwebs!
